snippet.textDisplay:
I shared this song with our nurses group, Antwerp, Belgium.
Our original posts were in the Cathlab, part of Cardiology. But when the call came we volunteered and divided ourselves to help out in the E.R and the Intensive Care Units.
Thank you for your song and thinking of us and al the other people working to keep people safe, fed, stocked and taken care off.
I also wanted to send out my love, sympathies and hopes for recovery and strength to the U.S.A(Always dear to my heart) and north America and the world in general. I do hope that if we beat this thing in Europe, we can send our help to you.
